comments:
The study was very interesting because I was engaged fully from start to finish. However, if it had lasted longer, my concentration would have been affected. The only strategies I used was remembering first the words/objects that are the easiest for me, associating them with words I use on daily basis, or they remind me of something. After I remembered those, then started remembering the ones that were more difficult.
Also, something unusual about the words, I had a feeling they were like 2-3 words that I already know, only their parts put together randomly, or like some anagrams etc.
